Class ProjectApplicationTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jb.couponsystem.ProjectApplicationTests

  • @SpringBootTest
public class ProjectApplicationTests
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains Spring Boot tests for the Coupon System application. FixMethodOrder: All the tests are running according to the ascending name order. RunWith: tests are run by SpringRunner class of the Spring Framework.

    Alexander Zablotsky

      • test_000_dailyThread

        public void test_000_dailyThread()
                          throws CouponAlreadyExistsException,
                                 java.lang.InterruptedException
        Test for daily thread. Creates new expired coupon in the database. Then creates an instance of the CouponSystem class which performs the daily task of removing the expired coupon from the database.
        Throws:
        CouponAlreadyExistsException - if the coupon exists in the database
        java.lang.InterruptedException - if the thread was interrupted
